::GoldenEye::

She flew out of the hatch with Dollen in her talons.  She flew out 
and away from the ship.  She saw Starscsream flying near the ship.
"HEY Starscream, where are you going to land?  We need to try to 
stick together on this. We'll be sitting ducks for those infuriating 
Maximals."

She glanced down at Dollen, "Comfy?"
